<!-- INTRO -->
<section class="intro">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="intro-inner reveal">
      <div class="intro-left">
        <p class="eyebrow">Our Philosophy</p>
        <h2 class="display">Dentistry<br>reimagined. <em>Entirely.</em></h2>
        <p class="body-copy">We started Ivory Haus because we believed something the industry had forgotten: your time in the dental chair should feel like an investment in yourself, not an interruption to your day.</p>
        <p class="body-copy">Every detail — the lighting, the materials, the technology, the conversation — has been curated with a singular intention. To make this the appointment you actually look forward to.</p>
        <blockquote class="intro-statement">"I wanted to change the narrative around dentistry entirely — to create a space where excellence and beauty exist in equal measure."<br><span style="font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;font-style:normal;opacity:.5;">— Dr. Cohlmia, Founder</span></blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-right">
        <div class="intro-stat">
          <p class="intro-stat-num">15<sup>+</sup></p>
          <p class="intro-stat-label">Years of Artistry</p>
        </div>
