<!-- SENSES -->
<section class="senses">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="senses-header reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow eyebrow-center">The Ivory Haus Experience</p>
      <h2 class="display">Designed for<br>every <em>sense</em></h2>
      <p class="body-copy">Your five senses have been thoughtfully considered at every touchpoint. We didn't build a dental office. We built a sanctuary.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="senses-grid reveal">
      <div class="sense-card">
        <div class="sense-glyph">◎</div>
        <p class="sense-name">Sight</p>
        <p class="sense-desc">Warm light, clean lines, and an aesthetic that feels more like a boutique than a clinic. Every surface was chosen with intention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sense-card">
        <div class="sense-glyph">♩</div>
        <p class="sense-name">Sound</p>
        <p class="sense-desc">A curated sonic environment — ambient, calm, and carefully tuned to dissolve any trace of clinical anxiety the moment you walk in.</p>
      </div>
